="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pULkm-3b_1M?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>最近几个月，Mk.gee 也受到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">埃里克·克莱普顿 (Eric Clapton)</a>的赞扬，他告诉 YouTuber <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=keBw11UZfEs" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Real Music Observer</em></a> ，他的音乐“对我来说属于流行音乐类别”，并且“它是独一无二的。他在吉他上找到了其他人无法比拟的东西。”</p><p> Clapton 还将 Mk.gee 的吉他技巧与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a>进行了比较，他说：“就像我第一次看到 Prince 时一样，就像我们很安全一样。只要知道它的存在就足够了”。</p><p> <em>NME</em>参加了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/mk-gee-london-electric-brixton-live-review-photos-setlist-radar-3808609">Mk.gee 最近在 Electric Brixton 为期三天的驻场演出的第一晚</a>。 “Mk.gee 的表演感觉就像一次聚会——一种近乎宗教的体验，一种对节奏的共同崇敬时刻，” <em>NME</em>的 Naz Hamdi 写道。</p><p> “就好像每个人都调到了一个更深的频率，被《多少英里》和《我想要》等歌曲中深情的连复段、风铃式的琴键和催眠的鼓声深深地吸引在一起。”</p><p> “这两首歌中敲出的每个音符都像是对个人而又集体的呼唤，音乐让人想起教堂集会——每次 Mk.gee 表演时，他都会通过一次添加每种乐器而不是编译来构建曲目。全部一起。”</p><p>他的现场表演也被证明是完全不可预测的——在最近的巡演中，Mk.gee <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mk-gee-cover-celine-dions-my-heart-will-go-on-and-andrea-bocellis-time-to-say-goodbye-in-philly-3811122">翻唱了席琳·迪翁的《My Heart Will Go On》和安德里亚·波切利的《Time To Say Goodbye》</a> ，他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mk-gee-played-his-song-dnm-12-times-during-one-show-in-minneapolis-3801160">演奏了 12 次《DNM》在一张歌单中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mk-gee-perform-alesis-and-rockman-on-saturday-night-live-3811319">观看 Mk.gee 在“周六夜现场”中表演“Alesis”和“ROCKMAN”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 André 3000 对长笛专辑《New Blue Sun》获得格莱美提名的反应：“我对此感到非常惊讶” https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-reacts-to-grammy-nominations-for-frude-album-new-blue-sun-i-was-totally-surprise-by-this- 3811300?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andre-3000-对长笛专辑新蓝色太阳的格莱美提名做出反应，对此我感到非常惊讶Daniel PetersSun, 10 Nov 2024 09:55:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsGrammysJazz https://www.nme.com/?p=3811300 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="André 300。图片来源：Taylor Hill/Getty Images for Live Nation Urban" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他的乐队 Outkast 凭借 2004 年的说唱专辑“Speakerboxxx/The Love Below”成为最后一位赢得年度专辑奖的艺人</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-reacts-to-grammy-nominations-for-flute-album-new-blue-sun-i-was-totally-surprised-by-this-3811300">André 3000 对长笛专辑《New Blue Sun》格莱美提名的反应：“我对此感到非常惊讶”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="André 300。图片来源：Taylor Hill/Getty Images for Live Nation Urban" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andre-3000">André 3000</a>对他的爵士乐专辑《New Blue Sun》获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">格莱美</a>提名做出了反应，这张专辑特别被选入年度专辑类别的竞争。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-romy-and-sampha-team-up-to-cover-andre-3000s-me-my-to-bury-your-parents-3598029">聆听 Romy 和 Sampha 合作翻唱 André 3000 的《Me &amp; My (To Bury Your Parent)》</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/11/08/arts/music/andre-3000-grammys-new-blue-sun.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/outkast">Outkast</a>成员（真名安德烈·本杰明）表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">上周五（11 月 8 日）提名公布</a>时，他刚刚在巡演中醒来。</p><p> “我们试图以某种方式获得另类爵士乐或氛围音乐的提名，”他承认。 “但我对此感到非常惊讶。所以是的，这真是超级、超级、超级酷。”</p><p>本杰明演奏长笛的器乐爵士专辑《New Blue Sun》已被提名为年度专辑、最佳另类爵士专辑以及专辑开场曲“I Swear, I Very Wanted to Make”的最佳器乐作品提名一张“说唱”专辑，但这一次确实是风吹我的方式。</p><p>采访者还向本杰明提到 Outkast 2004 年的热门专辑《Speakerboxxx/The Love Below》是最后一张赢得年度专辑的说唱专辑，他推测说唱对选民来说可能并不重要。</p><p> “我必须说，尽管《Speakerboxxx/The Love Below》是最后一张说唱专辑，但它只是半张说唱专辑。所以即便如此，这也表明，我们享受的不仅仅是说唱。” </p><figure id="attachment_3789267" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789267" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789267" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns.jpg" alt="Andre 3000 在挪威奥斯陆 Øyafestivalen 2024 上表演。图片来源：Per Ole Hagen/Redferns" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789267" class="wp-caption-text"> Andre 3000 在挪威奥斯陆 Øyafestivalen 2024 上表演。图片来源：Per Ole Hagen/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>本杰明与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">查莉·XCX</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jacob-collier">雅各布·科利尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>一起获得了颁奖典礼最高专辑奖的提名。请参阅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">此处</a>的完整提名列表。</p><p>八月，本杰明分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-andre-3000s-new-album-film-listening-to-the-sun-3789263"><em>《聆听太阳</em></a>》，这是一个以“新蓝太阳”音乐为特色的完整视觉效果——可以看到安德烈躺在一个神秘的蓝色房间里，深深地沉浸在他的专辑中。</p><p>今年早些时候，在解释“New Blue Sun”的新创作方向时，本杰明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-explains-why-he-stopped-rapping-3542363">承认他觉得自己已经脱离了开启他职业生涯的那种类型</a>：“有时我觉得说唱不真实，因为我没有任何事情都可以这样谈论。我今年 48 岁。这并不是说年龄决定了你说唱的内容，但在某种程度上确实如此。”</p><p>这一评论在说唱界引发了争议， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-on-ll-cool-j-telling-him-to-rap-again-im-not-trying-to-uphold-a-thing-ive-done-before-3775495">LL COOL J</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ja-rule">Ja Rule</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/killer-mike-responds-andre-3000-too-old-to-rap-2024-grammys-3582144">Killer Mike</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-wayne">Lil Wayne</a>等人都对他的决定表示失望。后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-its-so-depressing-that-andre-3000-said-hes-too-old-to-rap-3552410">表示，安德烈 3000 感觉“太老了”，无法说唱，这“太令人沮丧”了</a>，而 Ja Rule 则<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ja-rule-heartbroken-by-andre-3000-not-wanting-to-rap-anymore-lil-wayne-3574948">表示，这张专辑中“没有小节”让他“心碎”</a> 。</p><p>最近，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-announces-intimate-londons-jazz-cafe-performances-ahead-of-all-points-east-3779226">在伦敦进行了一场亲密的演出</a>，然后又<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-divides-fans-with-flute-performance-at-all-points-east-3784852">在 All Points East 进行了一场引起争议的演出</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-reacts-to-grammy-nominations-for-flute-album-new-blue-sun-i-was-totally-surprised-by-this-3811300">André 3000 对长笛专辑《New Blue Sun》格莱美提名的反应：“我对此感到非常惊讶”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
